    "body": "Given that it would require to go through all the widget templates and that it is doable in [v2 (which is in beta](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/)), I don't think we should move on with this PR.\r\n\r\nHowever we really greatly appreciate that you took the time to do the implementation and we hope that you will contribute again :)",
